n the US election in a very unhinged way", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-11T11:02:00+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"A first-person POV shot of the prow of a small boat as it sails through Caddo Lake in Max\u2019s sci-fi drama Caddo Lake\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Max\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/caroline-falk-eliza-scanlen.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\"><em>Caddo Lake</em>, the latest genre thriller dumped on Max with little fanfare (did you see <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/horror/458602/salems-lot-director-interview-stephen-king-2024-movie\"><em>Salem\u2019s Lot</em></a>?), veers toward the realistic end of the sci-fi movie spectrum. Set in a town of pickup trucks and local markets, where a close-knit community is treading water in a system that\u2019s not granting them any favors, <em>Caddo Lake </em>could easily be mistaken for a modern salt-of-the-earth drama. But as with <em>The Bab", "id": 1307777, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/review/464777/caddo-lake-streaming-max", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Caddo Lake is extremely produced by M. Night Shyamalan, if you get what I\u2019m saying", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-11T10:42:27+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/tomb_raider_4-6_remastered_lara_kick.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\"><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/24073332/tomb-raider-lara-croft-unified-design-artwork\">Lara Croft</a>\u2019s uneven second trilogy of games is getting remastered in 2025, with <em>Tomb Raider 4-6 Remastered</em>, Crystal Dynamics announced Friday. The collection will include updated versions of 1999\u2019s <em>Tomb Raider: The Last Revelation</em>, 2000\u2019s <em>Tomb Raider: Chronicles</em>, and 2003\u2019s <em>Tomb Raider: The Angel of Darkness</em>.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Like the well-regarded <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/24072218/tomb-raider-1-3-remastered-collection-review\"><em>Tomb Raider 1-3 Remastered</em></a> collection, the second tri", "id": 1307778, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/news/465121/tomb-raider-4-6-remastered-aspyr", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "The Tomb Raider that tried to kill off Lara Croft is getting a remaster", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-11T10:21:27+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image Composition: Ross Miller/Polygon | Source Images: Amazon, Microsoft\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/xbox-fire-tv-combo-custom.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">We\u2019ve written before about the Amazon Fire TV stick being one of the <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/amazon-prime-day/2024/7/17/24200649/fire-tv-4k-deal-xbox-game-pass-ultimate\">cheapest Xbox consoles</a>, so to speak \u2014\u00a0through the Xbox app on Fire TV, you can <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/best-games/22372750/best-game-pass-games-xbox\">stream hundreds of great titles</a> with an Xbox Game Pass Ultimate subscription. Well, it looks Amazon is formalizing that suggestion by now offering a veritable <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Amazon-Special-Wireless-Controller-Ultimate/dp/B0DGGG4", "id": 1307779, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/good-deals/465066/fire-tv-stick-xbox-game-pass-deal", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Experience the best of Xbox \u2014 without an Xbox \u2014 with this $80 starter kit", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-11T10:00:00+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/polygon-mosaic-2-1.png?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">People online are fessing up to their unconventional childhood crushes and I, for one, am happier because of it. A <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/tiktok\">new TikTok trend</a> has people making videos about their early love interests \u2014 like Diego from the Ice Age movies or The Man with the Yellow Hat from Curious George \u2014 with the <a href=\"https://tiktok